data.description: Beautiful white rock front home. You'll be hidden among the trees at the foot of the Hill Country. This secluded home is a one minute walk to Bullis Park and the new Timberwood Elem. Sch. The drive way is huge and features a two car air conditioned garage. You'll relax in the vaulted ceiling living room with the white rock fireplace. The huge master bedroom and guest bedroom boast high vaulted ceilings as well. The master has a Texas sized walk-in closet and tiled master bathroom with new granite counter tops. The kitchen is ready for any chief with new granite counter tops, new fridge, new stove, new double oven and walk-in pantry. The dinning room and breakfast nook have different beautiful views to the incredible yards. The back yard is heavily shaded with a walking trail, BBQ area, huge screened in covered patio with new hot tub, and many beautiful plants. The front and back yard has an automated sprinkler system. The entire back yard is in-closed with an 8' fence and includes a huge 200 square foot vegetable garden.
data.whatILove: The back yard is like a park with huge trees, walking trail, vegetable garden, grilling area and a large screened in porch with a new hot tub.
